text: Delhi: Sapna & Sanjay, a couple has been living on the streets near Jantar Mantar, even as country is under lockdown. Sanjay says, "We have exhausted our rations & don't know what will happen now. My wife is 8 months pregnant, my heart aches that she has to go hungry". #COVID19 https://t.co/3swhgQQl4F
